AWS services
============
EC2: virtual servers
S3 : Simple storage services : unlimited storage 
RDS : relational database services => RDBMS
IAM : Identity and access management  => Users, groups and roles 
VPC : Virtual private cloud => network
Route 53: DNS -> domain mapping
EKS -> Elastic kubernetes service
Lambdas : serverless computing --> run your application without thinking abt server 
cloud watch : monitor resourcs 
Beanstack : platform as a service 


NOTE: 

when join  a organisation ,  you will login as a IAM user .




